title: Cool but strange video I came upon

embed.description: The final part of the Summer Series. Enjoy :) (Some bad puns and jazz enjoy) Music: Remady & Manu-L - Holidays Money Money Money Beach Sounds

body: Hey Guys , I was just searching the internet one night when I found this video, quite strange but the guy is actually pretty decent, check it out pretty funny.

replies.body:
I'm not saying anything but....

He is a massive, if not the largest, Dunkey wannabe. He lacks any "originality" and copies Dunkey, from the way he talks to even his main quotes (e.g. Saying "Baby" 100% how dunkey does and "(champion name here) do you really think you can escape me" just to name a few). I'm not saying his video's aren't high quality though, and for the most part funny.  However, almost 100% of the stuff he says and the way he acts was copped of from one of the Dunkeys videos just puts it in the category "So bad its funny".

He would probably be a good and funny YouTube channel if he just acted himself, rather then copping off someone else. Anyway, rage train is over.
-GL,HF
